292
00:19:08,940 --> 00:19:09,340
Although

293
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:10,500
I don't know why

294
00:19:12,780 --> 00:19:14,420
you lied to me
about your father's death,

295
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:15,420
when you

296
00:19:15,420 --> 00:19:16,300
told me

297
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:19,620
that your father was still alive,

298
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:23,540
(I felt quite happy for you.)

299
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:28,100
(I couldn't joke )

300
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:30,180
(about someone's death.)

301
00:19:33,300 --> 00:19:34,100
And I didn't know

302
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:36,820
how to part with them.

303
00:19:39,100 --> 00:19:39,660
Why is there someone

304
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:41,300
as foolish as you?

305
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,340
Am I really that foolish?

306
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:51,020
Yes.

307
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:58,860
Feng Tianlan.

308
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:02,580
Actually, I'm not

309
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:03,900
as free-spirited as you think I am.

310
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:06,500
If I could,

311
00:20:07,300 --> 00:20:08,620
I want to live
a free and easy life, too.

312
00:20:13,940 --> 00:20:15,100
Although my dad is still alive,

313
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:17,860
he's indeed ill.

314
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:23,580
And his condition is getting worse.

315
00:20:26,180 --> 00:20:27,780
So I still need to go back.

316
00:20:29,260 --> 00:20:30,860
I didn't lie to you about that.

317
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:37,660
Maybe,

318
00:20:39,620 --> 00:20:41,260
I was using you as an excuse.

319
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,860
I thought if you didn't drive me back,

320
00:20:47,260 --> 00:20:48,500
I wouldn't have to go back.

321
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:52,540
Who knows

322
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:55,540
that you didn't even say no to this?

323
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:04,340
Feng Tianlan.

324
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:09,180
Actually, we are just ordinary people.

325
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:13,060
We'll all die one day.

326
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:17,820
But we are living

327
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:19,620
as if we had forever together.

328
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:22,620
(Getting to know someone is easy.)

329
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:25,540
(But it's never easy
to say goodbye properly.)

330
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,940
(We'll meet some,)

331
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:33,580
(and we'll part ways with some.)

332
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:37,260
We don't have to care

333
00:21:38,140 --> 00:21:39,100
or think too much about it.

334
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:49,900
Don't you have anything else to say

335
00:21:50,380 --> 00:21:51,420
except nodding yes?

336
00:21:52,020 --> 00:21:53,300
I said so much.

337
00:21:54,060 --> 00:21:54,700
All you ever say

338
00:21:55,380 --> 00:21:55,820
to me is,

339
00:21:55,940 --> 00:21:57,300
"Okay, Ms. Wang"

340
00:21:57,300 --> 00:21:58,820
"You eat too much, Ms. Wang"

341
00:21:58,820 --> 00:22:00,340
and "Don't do this, Ms. Wang".

342
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:03,820
I bully you every day.

343
00:22:03,820 --> 00:22:04,900
But you still put up with me.

344
00:22:05,300 --> 00:22:06,500
Could it be that you like me?

345
00:22:08,260 --> 00:22:08,860
Yes.

346
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:12,140
Do I like you?

347
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:15,060
Or not?

348
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:21,660
Maybe I do.

